</span><span class='line'>jekyll 3.1.2 | Error:  jekyll-paginate</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>


<h3>解决方法</h3>

<p>我们安装这个插件到本地即可。</p>

<figure class='code'><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class=''><span class='line'>gem install jekyll-paginate
</span><span class='line'>Fetching: jekyll-paginate-1.1.0.gem (100%)
</span><span class='line'>Successfully installed jekyll-paginate-1.1.0
</span><span class='line'>Parsing documentation for jekyll-paginate-1.1.0
</span><span class='line'>Installing ri documentation for jekyll-paginate-1.1.0
</span><span class='line'>Done installing documentation for jekyll-paginate after 3 seconds
</span><span class='line'>1 gem installed</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>



]]></content>
